Alliance Rises to Three-Week High on Citigroup’s ‘Buy’ Rating

-- B y   I a n   S a y s o n
-- 
2011-10-12T04:47:17Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-12/alliance-rises-to-three-week-high-on-citigroup-s-buy-rating.html
Alliance Global Group Inc. (AGI)  advanced
to a three-week high in Manila after the stock was rated “buy”
with a 12-month share-price estimate of 12 pesos in initial
coverage by Citigroup Inc.  The stock climbed as much as 3 percent to 9.79 pesos and
traded at 9.72 pesos at 12:46 p.m., heading for the highest
close since Sept. 22. The benchmark Philippine Stock Exchange
Index was little changed.   To contact the reporter on this story:
Ian Sayson in Manila at 
 isayson@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Matthew Oakley at 
 moakley@bloomberg.net  